Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hurt my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:01:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:02:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Pacifista!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Mystery Deepens!\NEgghead Labophase"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is it true that Kuma is your father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Why would I lie to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you came to see Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alright! I only did it to buy time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonney! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't buy us much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Subdue them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonney, I'm sorry but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...I gotta stop him by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Bonney.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You two, don't drop your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Egghead, Vegapunk's island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's different from\Nthe Pacifistas we know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Subdue the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...m-my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...is paralyzed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Chopper! You guys became decrepit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You became...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He no longer recognized us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's escape while we still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My back hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That Pacifista suddenly stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Bonney...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:04.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,LUFFY, 70 YEARS OLD (IN A POSSIBLE FUTURE)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have disguised me as a better age...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you don't let us bust up the ones\Nwho are not your dad, we'll be in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Bonney.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been through a lot\Nwith the Pacifistas so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And turn me back to my original self...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they are clones of someone\Nwho originally was a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it stands to reason that he'd have a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get offended, Bonney.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What I know about Kuma is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...that he was an evil king of\Nthe Sorbet Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...who was expelled by its citizens,\Nand then became a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,After becoming a member of\Nthe Revolutionary Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he was arrested by the Navy\Nand sentenced to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But because Vegapunk was deeply interested\Nin his physique and potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,he was allowed to return to sea\Nas one of the Seven Warlords...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...on the condition that he submits himself\Nto body augmentation and cloning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Warlord and cloning parts add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But not the cyborg part.\NThat's like the death penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would accept it\Nif they knew that's what it's all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are different kinds\Nof life sentences.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what crimes\NKuma the Tyrant committed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My father wasn't a tyrant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't like the World Government!\NThere's no way he'd cooperate with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He must've been forcibly modified!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you trying to kill us?!\NThat was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A beam saber?! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a scrap heap...\NThese are the scraps of Vegapunk's inventions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, this is murder\Nin the name of science!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My father said\Nhe came from a special tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't give them\Nthe right to experiment on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't give them\Nthe right to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A special tribe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonney...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you turn me back, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The robot is flying in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Vegapunk's island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If we tell Luffy and Chopper\Nthat we flew in the sky by giant robot,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll be jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How could such a huge thing fly so high?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's anti-gravity.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This Vegaforce-01 is\Npropelled by the jets on its back,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and kept afloat by an anti-gravity device.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Anti-gravity"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The air conditioning on this island makes it possible,\Nbut it may be all over the world someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Look at that city!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen buildings like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there is a monster! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a giant robot! How many are there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fish are flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because of the anti-gravity device?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a futuristic city!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an island where the future is made!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Future Island Egghead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Above the clouds is the laboratory level,\NLabophase!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Down there is the factory level,\NFabriophase!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Workers and researchers live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your captain is messing around\Ndown there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to know he's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help getting excited!\NWhat do I get to see next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Zoro, aren't you coming?!\NAnd you, Brook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'll look after the ship.\N--Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?! It's a futuristic island!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't trust that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, that fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilith-{\i1}chan{\i}!\NYou can just forget about that stupid Mosshead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,--What is it?\N--Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Try what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--The surface is like the Sky Island!\N--Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? This is the first time for me!\NWhat's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this also Vegapunk's handiwork?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! You guessed right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,By perfectly controlling\Nthe air conditioning on the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to modify the density of Pyrobloin\Nand moisture in the condensation nuclei,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and recreate the Island Clouds\Nand Sea Clouds of the Sky Islands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess wasn't that sophisticated!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the entrance of the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Showy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Change to lab clothes before entering!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trancos on the sides\Nare changing rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of clothes there are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Future, future! Can't wait, can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--I wonder what kind of clothes they have!\N--Can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I leave Nami-{\i1}san{\i} and Robin-{\i1}chan{\i} alone\Nat an unfamiliar place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a duty to watch them closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm doing this. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools who slight ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the fool! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Choose the clothes you like.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The clothes I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we push these buttons?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull the levers on your Dom Shoes yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll fit any type of foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,These, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They look heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So light!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin, you look great in them!\NIt's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They can strangle a wearer to death\Nif they want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say such a scary thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited in these futuristic outfits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk is impressive!\NThey fit perfectly even on my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Super{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:14:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just an aloha shirt\Nno matter how you look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i} and Robin-{\i1}chan{\i} are cute,\Nso it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen this fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin, you look great and strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a pervert no matter what you wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too much of a compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you have to go with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Government island.\NWho will help them if they get caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You misters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We already left the Land of Wano long ago.\NGoodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I did get a ride on the condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...that the destination would be anywhere\Noutside the Land of Wano...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But not here, mister!\NIt's a Government island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for helping our captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make these fools pay!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The stairs are moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The stairs are pouring out from the bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the mechanism? What powers it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of power on this island is fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire can be converted\Nto all forms of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there a lot of resources here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been researching what I should burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I could even make a sun\Nif only there was a flame that wouldn't go out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A sun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're in our way!\N--Franky, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're walking into a wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a wall, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,--Open it!\N--Lilith-{\i1}chan{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Just walk through it!\NDon't be fooled by what you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lilith! Lilith!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Edison?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilith-{\i1}chan{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear anything now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,His neck! His head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. If his head has been cut off,\Nthere would be a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for a sober analysis! You scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just walk through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't look so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:16:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,--Alright.\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'll go, too.\N--H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I came through...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did they make it so confusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! It's just an iron door\Nafter we made it through! How does it work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilith-{\i1}chan{\i}'s gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Walk straight ahead!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm Vegapunk Edison!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Vegapunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm glad you made it.\NJust follow my lead.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still straight ahead.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Turn right there.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Turn left.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta hunt for "future treasure"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's "future treasure"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like flowers made of gemstones!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell if that's childish\Nor old-fashioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Future Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,--What's this place?\N--Is this a dead end?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They look like doors...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll open it for you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--Hey! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimbei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's too young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And he looks different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The first possibility. Jimbei's child!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The second possibility.\NJimbei was turned into a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The third possibility.\NJimbei's look-alike!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He has wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And he has a strange vibe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks like a kid, but as big as Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth possibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A Pacifista!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Geniuses can even see their own future...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you talking about, Vegapunk?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:56.11,On Top,,0,0,0,,GOOD
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...will die soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop joking! That's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted you to know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:21.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:28.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:35.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:42.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:49.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:56.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:21:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:21:05.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:11.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:18.27,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:25.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:32.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:39.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Tell Me, Robin!\NChopper's I-Wanna-Learn-More-You-Fool!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! I'm Chopper,\Nthe ship's doctor of the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Robin, an archaeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.85,0:21:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin, I can't wait to learn as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Information can be a strong weapon.\NLet's keep learning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Today we'll learn about this one!\NBartholomew Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a pirate and a former Warlord of the Sea\Nwho is also known as "the Tyrant."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a Paw-Paw Fruit power-user...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...which enables him\Nto repel anything with his paw pads,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and send it flying over great distances.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born on February 9th\Nand likes honey and salmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.96,0:22:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He was one of the Seven Warlords,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but he was also actually an officer of\Nthe Revolutionary Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.38,0:22:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a fight once with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but he saved us from Kizaru and Sentomaru.\NWe owe him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an officer of the Revolutionary Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a connection with them,\Nand I want to help them get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.19,0:22:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuma was being modified into a cyborg\Nlittle by little by the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but before he lost his free will,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,he made a request\Nto be programmed to protect the Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.13,0:23:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And he completely lost his free will\Nbefore the Paramount War.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.51,0:23:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why he had to become a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.63,0:23:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for this week! See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.89,0:23:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The possibilities of science are infinite!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The research has already begun!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.15,0:23:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their unfathomable spirit of inquiry\Noverwhelms the Straw Hats.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good and evil. Wisdom and greed.\NAn idea and an explosion.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Talented minds overflowing\Nfrom all directions now gather here!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"The Brain of a Genius - Six Vegapunks!"
